  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1-\u0b95\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1-\u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe/175-299807",
  "time_ut": 1657054945,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe ?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another Black July?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "JVP leader Anurakumara Dissanayake said in the House that there are suspicions that the government is planning to create violence like Black July to divert the people's protests against the government.",
        "He said this in his speech during the debate on the Prime Minister's speech in Parliament yesterday (5). Then he added,",
        "A letter has been sent to the Security Secretary of the Inspector General of Police on the 27th. In it, it is mentioned that a bomb attack will be carried out by a foreign intelligence agency in the North or South, similar to what the LTTE did on the 5th and 6th of the Black Tigers Memorial Day.",
        "Has the cabinet discussed this issue? Has it been discussed in the Security Council? If not, does the Inspector General of Police think this? This cannot be taken for granted. This was the period when the uprisings against the government took place. At this time, the Inspector General of Police has sent a letter to the Defense Minister regarding such an attack.",
        "At this time Manusha Nanayakkara MP said that on the 9th, big vehicles may burn and houses may burn. There are doubts about this. Doubts arise that the government itself is planning to do chaotic work to stop the protests against the government. We ask whether they are planned and implemented to divert protests against the government.",
        "During the 80's there was another army of Rural Defense Force. There are also doubts about the beginning in such a situation. It seems that the government is trying to create incidents by planning accordingly. This happened in 1983.",
        "Tamils \u200b\u200bwere set on fire in Chettiar Street. Attacks were carried out on those who opposed the government. Similarly they created Black July. Is the government trying to recreate such violence? He said that doubts arise."
      ],
